Creatures of this alignment have total disdain and scorn for life, 
beauty, truth, and freedom.  Their only purpose is total conquest
of the world through any means necessary, most likely at the expense 
of others.  They also believe in the total eradication of good creatures
and often capture and manipulate them into being their slaves.  It is 
extremely rare for a normal creature to become this evil without some 
supernatural or magical assistance.
